www.tokemak.xyz/>\\n6\\\\.其他的仿盘很多 ，可以看 推特@Uncle_DeFi 整理的列表，风险自行评估\\n\\n七、顶级投资机构\\n1\\\\.a16z. <https://a16z.com/>\\n2\\\\.padadigm <https://www.paradigm.xyz/>\\n3\\\\.三箭资本. <https://www.threearrowscap.com>\\n4\\\\. multicoin. <https://multicoin.capital/>\\n5\\\\. Alameda <https://www.alameda-research.com/>\\n6\\\\. R8 <http://www.r8.capital/>\\n7\\\\. 另附 <https://mirror.xyz/bigsir.eth/alBYmPMMdggQYsDDwfL-ZsN-csOnySPVgyci9i8f1j8> 链闻专栏 <https://www.chainnews.com/tag_14466.htm>\\n\\n持续学习，终身成长！\",\"timestamp\":1636382809,\"title\":\"币圈进阶之路\"},\"digest\":\"q_Sy1OLjMDwT95Y9RELdTD_c4uyQOc9__OszBWkUFAw\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x232d6af618e257485C1D29cc75F35AA6D4d760B1\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"1OeCjwV8HFp5OkLPhBzg545evVh4UA6Z0RNCOeR8YaA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"_BGmshrfkTIhpDUDoDGLseBli2cK29is7tiy1UM39e8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"zRb6Ch2ZmbvQvocw4NT7_AFEepg5W-9Qx-LJqI3Bppcw1ns6uM3gWf_y8TAhOAEaVlswaeO30Fubdm315Ca3Hg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb386520c23a77f7ab4057fee07cdb5098e038e3bd7f576caf48a7089167f39bc7818a77dd6ca086718f9b9a55cd77f00901cdadcc8642d6fdcd0ad049be78ad71b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"1OeCjwV8HFp5OkLPhBzg545evVh4UA6Z0RNCOeR8YaA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"_BGmshrfkTIhpDUDoDGLseBli2cK29is7tiy1UM39e8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"q_Sy1OLjMDwT95Y9RELdTD_c4uyQOc9__OszBWkUFAw\"}"